# Portfolio — Figma ↔ Code design system

This site is a **static HTML / CSS / JavaScript** portfolio. There is **no React, Vue, or Tailwind build**. Layout chrome is injected by `PortfolioApp` in `assets/js/components.js` using string templates from `assets/js/layout-components.js`. Case study bodies live in `#page-specific-content` inside each `*.html` file.

## Design tokens (source of truth: CSS variables)

Tokens are defined in `assets/css/style.css` on `:root` and overridden under `[data-theme="dark"]`.

| Figma variable (suggested name) | Light | Dark | CSS variable |
|----------------------------------|-------|------|--------------|
| `color/bg/default` | `#ffffff` | `#121212` | `--bg-color` |
| `color/text/primary` | `#111111` | `#ffffff` | `--text-color` |
| `color/text/secondary` | `#555555` | `#aaaaaa` | `--secondary-text` |
| `color/border/default` | `#e0e0e0` | `#333333` | `--border-color` |
| `color/accent/primary` | `#2ecc71` | *(unchanged)* | `--accent-color` |
| `color/accent/hover` | `#27ae60` | *(use for filled button hover)* | *(see `.projects-cta-btn:hover`)* |

**Semantic / decorative (not all are variables — mirror in Figma as needed):**

- Image placeholder surface: `#eee` / `#e0e0e0`; placeholder text: `#777` / `#888`
- Overlay gradient on project tiles: `linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.34) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.96) 100%)`
- Accent wash (cards, callouts): `rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.06)` … `0.12` (grep `rgba(46, 204, 113` in `style.css`)
- Case-study alt section (light theme): `#f8f9fa` (see `.case-section-alt`)
- Playful shapes (home CTA / cards): green `#2ecc71`, blue `#4A55E0`, yellow `#E8E258`
- Brand mark (logo SVG text): `#2ecc71` (`LayoutComponents.logoSVG` in `layout-components.js`)
- Footer “green” variant: background `--accent-color`, text `#000000` with black-tinted borders (see `.site-footer-green`)

**Layout tokens (CSS):**

- `--header-height`: `60px` (mobile header `50px` in media queries)
- `--footer-height`: `50px`
- Content max width for case studies: `900px` (`.case-section-inner`, `.case-content`)

**Border radius (Figma corner styles):**

- `4px` — scrollbar thumb
- `8px` — primary cards / images (`.image-container`, `.visit-btn`, `.next-project-img`)
- `12px` — tables, pills in some case pages (`.case-table`; case pages may add `12px` in scoped CSS)
- `20px` — filter buttons, some tags
- `999` (full pill) — nav home button, back button, CTA pills, overlay tags

**Spacing (common values to mirror as Figma spacing variables):** `4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 15, 16, 18, 20, 24, 25, 28, 30, 40, 56, 60, 72` (px). Grid gaps: project grid `30px`; next projects `24px`.

