- **Weights in use:** 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 900 (see `.case-section-title`, `.hero-text h1`, `.nav-link`, etc.).
- **Representative text styles (create Figma styles with these names):**

| Style name | Approx size | Weight | Notes |
|------------|-------------|--------|--------|
| `Display / Hero` | `3.5rem` (~56px) | 800 | Sidebar project title `.hero-text h1` |
| `Heading / Section` | `1.75rem`–`1.8rem` | 800 | Case section title, CTA title |
| `Heading / Next project` | `1.5rem` | 800 | `.next-projects-title` |
| `Title / Card overlay` | `1.55rem` | 800 | `.project-overlay-title` |
| `Label / Uppercase` | `0.65rem`–`0.8rem` | 700 | Nav, meta labels, tags, uppercase buttons |
| `Body / Default` | `1rem` | 400–500 | Paragraphs; line-height ~1.65–1.8 |
| `Body / Small` | `0.85rem`–`0.92rem` | 400 | Subtitles, secondary |

